OL,3,GOPINIONCTV Licence increase and the
OL,4,Cfaux outrage from the usual suspects
OL,5,
OL,6,FYou don't need to believe the BBC is
OL,7,Fperfect to think that 50p a day is
OL,8,Fremarkable value for money.
OL,10,FThe Times on Saturday costs #4 ` or 8
OL,11,Fdays of viewing and listening.
OL,13,FThe daily fee is cheaper than a pint of
OL,14,Fmilk or bar of chocolate. The weekly
OL,15,Fcost is less than that of a coffee at
OL,16,Fmany coffee shops.
