OL,3,GOPINIONCTV Licence increase and the
OL,4,Cfaux outrage from the usual suspects
OL,5,
OL,6,FOf course, there is a principle. We
OL,7,Fchoose to buy newspapers or decent cups
OL,8,Fof coffee. We pay a licence fee for
OL,9,Fbeing in possession of a television `
OL,10,Feven if you never watch BBC TV, listen
OL,11,Fto BBC Radio or use the iPlayer and
OL,12,Fother online services.
OL,14,FI have yet to meet a person who doesn't
OL,15,Fuse BBC services at all who is neither
OL,16,Fmaking a point nor mildly eccentric. I
OL,17,Feven met someone recently who told me
OL,18,Fthey refused to watch the BBC while
OL,19,Fthey were tuned to Bargain Hunt. Don't
OL,20,Fask.
OL,23,EPub: 08-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
