OL,3,GOPINIONCTV Licence increase and the
OL,4,Cfaux outrage from the usual suspects
OL,5,
OL,6,FAnd all of us who support public
OL,7,Fservice broadcasting can talk until we
OL,8,Fare blue in the face about how the BBC
OL,9,Fis one of the building blocks of
OL,10,Fsociety.
OL,12,FThink about all that would be lost if
OL,13,Fall TV and radio output was simply
OL,14,Fdesigned to get ratings or deliver an
OL,15,Faudience to advertisers.
OL,17,FThink of all the jobs in creative
OL,18,Findustries across the UK. The work
OL,19,Fgiven to countless people -musicians,
OL,20,Factors, writers and others who don't
OL,21,Fwork in broadcasting as such.
