OL,3,GOPINIONCTV Licence increase and the
OL,4,Cfaux outrage from the usual suspects
OL,5,
OL,6,FOf course, there is a big issue to
OL,7,Fdiscuss. Are there realistic
OL,8,Falternatives to the TV Licence?
OL,10,FWe all know there is no realistic
OL,11,Fchance of the current government going
OL,12,Ffor either commercial funding or
OL,13,Fsubscription for existing BBC services.
OL,14,FDirect funding from general taxation is
OL,15,Falready, rightly, ruled out on
OL,16,Fprinciple.
OL,18,FThe government is essentially doing
OL,19,Fblue sky thinking about alternatives.
OL,23,EPub: 08-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
