OL,3,GOPINIONCTV Licence increase and the
OL,4,Cfaux outrage from the usual suspects
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe idea of a household levy charged
OL,7,Falong with the council tax is an
OL,8,Fattractive one with merits.
OL,10,FThere would be some link to ability to
OL,11,Fpay and it would be harder to avoid.
OL,13,FBut there are difficulties. For a
OL,14,Fstart, the council tax is not levied in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,17,FWe know there will be another rise in
OL,18,Fthe licence fee next year in line with
OL,19,Finflation. Hopefully, inflation will be
OL,20,Fclose to the Bank of England's 2pc
OL,21,Ftarget by then.
OL,23,EPub: 08-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
