OL,3,GOPINIONCTV Licence increase and the
OL,4,Cfaux outrage from the usual suspects
OL,5,
OL,6,FThen what? I simply cannot see how an
OL,7,Falternative to the licence fee can be
OL,8,Fagreed and implemented as early as
OL,9,F2028.
OL,11,FFor the same reason, I cannot see any
OL,12,Frealistic way of switching off Freeview
OL,13,Fby 2033 or 34. Not unless the
OL,14,Fgovernment spends a fortune on internet
OL,15,Faccess and some sort of TV adapter for
OL,16,Fthe vulnerable.
OL,18,FUltimately any decision to switch off
OL,19,FFreeview is for the government ` not
OL,20,Fthe BBC or any other public service
OL,21,Fbroadcaster.
OL,23,EPub: 08-Feb-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
