OL,3,GOPINIONCTV Licence increase and the
OL,4,Cfaux outrage from the usual suspects
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt is very important that the
OL,7,Fgovernment should give an unambiguous
OL,8,Fstatement soon.
OL,10,FSwitching off Freeview can only be
OL,11,Fcontemplated when only a small number
OL,12,Fof people are using it.
OL,14,FTwo bets.
OL,16,FThe TV Licence will still be with us in
OL,17,F2028 even if it may be modified.
OL,19,FAnd Freeview will be around for a long
OL,20,Ftime too -even just for resilience and
OL,21,Fthe vulnerable.
